Nice find. Considering the bug is literally staring every single user in the face on the URL bar, I would imagine it would be hard to pin blame on an individual.<p>I guess this is the final nail in the coffin for the &#x27;many eyes&#x27; theory though.<p>At least it will make a good t-shirt;<p><pre><code>  &quot;Query String Parameters Are Not Private&quot;
  &quot;Friends Don&#x27;t Let Friends Store PHI in Query Parameters&quot;
</code></pre>
OK, never mind about the t-shirt.
